OL,6,     GAnderson in conversation with
OL,7,     Gballet superstar Rudolf Nureyev.
OL,8,     GFirst broadcast in 1974.
OL,9,G0020FNature: The Classical Collection
OL,10,     GThe natural world has always been
OL,11,     Ga powerful inspiration to
OL,12,     Gcomposers, and this programme
OL,13,     Gtakes us on an evocative journey
OL,14,     Gthrough some of the best-loved
OL,15,     Gmusical responses.
